(0/n) Convert Audio to WAVE
===========================

MKV
---
mkvextract tracks foo.mkv 0:foo.ogg
opusdec foo.ogg foo.wav

MP3
---
ffmpeg -i foo.mp3 foo.wav

(1/n) Convert Audio to 16kHz mono
=================================

sox foo.wav -r 16000 -c 1 foo_16m.wav


Split Audio into Segments
=========================

./abook-segment.py foo_16m.wav


MKV to WAV audio track extraction
=================================

mkvextract tracks ccall/2018-02-08_15-30-28-guenter-marc.mkv 0:foo.ogg
opusdec foo.ogg telco201802081530.wav
./abook-segment.py telco201802081530.wav

